</li>
<li data-start="8627" data-end="8681">
<p data-start="8629" data-end="8681">advection term: coherence moved by propagation flows</p>
</li>
<li data-start="8682" data-end="8729">
<p data-start="8684" data-end="8729"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>α</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">Φ</mi><mi>S</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">-\alpha\Phi S</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.7667em; vertical-align: -0.0833em;"></span><span class="mord">−</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.0037em;">α</span><span class="mord">Φ</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.05764em;">S</span></span></span></span>: entropy corrodes coherence</p>
</li>
