<li data-start="9639" data-end="9736">
<p data-start="9641" data-end="9736"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>μ</mi><mi mathvariant="script">M</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\mu\mathcal{M}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.8778em; vertical-align: -0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">μ</span><span class="mord mathcal">M</span></span></span></span>: mutation injection (noise, adversaries, translation loss, memetic mutation)</p>
