<li data-start="9737" data-end="9826">
<p data-start="9739" data-end="9826"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>λ</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">Φ</mi><mi>S</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">-\lambda\Phi S</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.7778em; vertical-align: -0.0833em;"></span><span class="mord">−</span><span class="mord mathnormal">λ</span><span class="mord">Φ</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.05764em;">S</span></span></span></span>: coherence suppresses entropy (standards, proofs, canon, redundancy)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="9828" data-end="9876">This system encodes the SITH story in RSVP form:</p>
<ul data-start="9877" data-end="10034">
<li data-start="9877" data-end="9918">
<p data-start="9879" data-end="9918">living = coherent attractor in <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">Φ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\Phi</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord">Φ</span></span></span></span></p>
