</li>
<li data-start="2541" data-end="2596">
<p data-start="2543" data-end="2596"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">S</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.05764em;">S</span></span></span></span>: suppressed by procedure, versioning, precedent</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2598" data-end="2610">This is why:</p>
<ul data-start="2611" data-end="2711">
<li data-start="2611" data-end="2639">
<p data-start="2613" data-end="2639">revolutions burn archives,</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2640" data-end="2665">
<p data-start="2642" data-end="2665">coups seize ministries,</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2666" data-end="2711">
<p data-start="2668" data-end="2711">empires collapse when record-keeping fails.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2713" data-end="2757">Destroy the furniture and the organism dies.</p>
<hr data-start="2759" data-end="2762">
<h2 data-start="2764" data-end="2817">3. Junk Drawer vs Bureau = Evolutionary Speciation</h2>
<p data-start="2819" data-end="2862">This gives you a clean evolutionary ladder:</p>
<div class="TyagGW_tableContainer"><div tabindex="-1" class="group TyagGW_tableWrapper flex flex-col-reverse w-fit"><table data-start="2864" data-end="3299" class="w-fit min-w-(--thread-content-width)"><thead data-start="2864" data-end="2908"><tr data-start="2864" data-end="2908"><th data-start="2864" data-end="2876" data-col-size="sm">Structure</th><th data-start="2876" data-end="2890" data-col-size="sm">RSVP Regime</th><th data-start="2890" data-end="2908" data-col-size="sm">SITH Life Type</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start="2951" data-end="3299"><tr data-start="2951" data-end="3020"><td data-start="2951" data-end="2965" data-col-size="sm">Junk drawer</td><td data-start="2965" data-end="2992" data-col-size="sm">High <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">S</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.05764em;">S</span></span></span></span>, low <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">Φ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\Phi</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord">Φ</span></span></span></span></td><td data-start="2992" data-end="3020" data-col-size="sm">Proto-life / exploratory</td></tr><tr data-start="3021" data-end="3075"><td data-start="3021" data-end="3030" data-col-size="sm">Folder</td><td data-start="3030" data-end="3050" data-col-size="sm">Moderate <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">Φ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\Phi</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord">Φ</span></span></span></span></td><td data-start="3050" data-end="3075" data-col-size="sm">Differentiated tissue</td></tr><tr data-start="3076" data-end="3137"><td data-start="3076" data-end="3093" data-col-size="sm">Filing cabinet</td><td data-start="3093" data-end="3128" data-col-size="sm">High <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">Φ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\Phi</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord">Φ</span></span></span></span>, stable <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover accent="true"><mi>v</mi><mo>⃗</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec v</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.714em;"></span><span class="mord accent"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height: 0.714em;"><span style="top: -3em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height: 3em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.03588em;">v</span></span><span style="top: -3em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height: 3em;"></span><span class="accent-body" style="left: -0.2077em;"><span class="overlay" style="height: 0.714em; width: 0.471em;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="0.471em" height="0.714em" viewBox="0 0 471 714" preserveAspectRatio="xMinYMin" style="width: 0.471em;"><path d="M377 20c0-5.333 1.833-10 5.5-14S391 0 397 0c4.667 0 8.667 1.667 12 5
