<hr data-start="1906" data-end="1909">
<h3 data-start="1911" data-end="1949">3.3 Seating → vector field shaping</h3>
<p data-start="1950" data-end="1969">Seating determines:</p>
<ul data-start="1970" data-end="2043">
<li data-start="1970" data-end="1982">
<p data-start="1972" data-end="1982">adjacency,</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1983" data-end="1997">
<p data-start="1985" data-end="1997">eye contact,</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1998" data-end="2020">
<p data-start="2000" data-end="2020">conversational flow,</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2021" data-end="2043">
<p data-start="2023" data-end="2043">coalition formation.</p>
</li>
</ul>
