<p data-start="6161" data-end="6234"><strong data-start="6161" data-end="6195">Furniture as Operators in SITH</strong>, written in continuous academic prose,</p>
</li>
<li data-start="6235" data-end="6385">
<p data-start="6237" data-end="6385">culminating in a detailed, formal analysis of <strong data-start="6283" data-end="6315">“The Room Where It Happened”</strong> as a bounded semantic environment that stabilizes political outcomes.</p>
</li>
</ul>
