<h3 data-start="3654" data-end="3696">Notes (not for inclusion in the paper)</h3>
<ul data-start="3697" data-end="4080">
<li data-start="3697" data-end="3775">
<p data-start="3699" data-end="3775">This bibliography is <strong data-start="3720" data-end="3754">deliberately interdisciplinary</strong> but not scattershot.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="3776" data-end="3931">
