</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="4707" data-end="4710">
<h2 data-start="4712" data-end="4763">5. One Clarifying Question (The Only One I Need)</h2>
<p data-start="4765" data-end="4818">Before proceeding, I need a single decision from you:</p>
