This message provides the <strong data-start="102" data-end="139">intermediate-scale worked example</strong> that bridges abstract formalism and architectural operators. It is written as continuous academic prose and is now <strong data-start="255" data-end="268">canonical</strong>; later sections on furniture and rooms will explicitly rely on it.</p>
