<h2 data-start="3581" data-end="3624">Pattern to follow everywhere (important)</h2>
<p data-start="3626" data-end="3668">From here on, use <strong data-start="3644" data-end="3667">this invariant rule</strong>:</p>
<blockquote data-start="3670" data-end="3799">
<p data-start="3672" data-end="3799">❌ <code data-start="3674" data-end="3682">(\Phi)</code>, <code data-start="3684" data-end="3694">(\vec v)</code>, <code data-start="3696" data-end="3701">(S)</code><br data-start="3701" data-end="3704">
✅ “the coherence potential $\Phi$”, “the propagation field $\vec v$”, “the entropy field $S$”</p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="3801" data-end="3813">This avoids:</p>
<ul data-start="3814" data-end="3910">
<li data-start="3814" data-end="3831">
<p data-start="3816" data-end="3831">overfull boxes,</p>
</li>
<li data-start="3832" data-end="3856">
<p data-start="3834" data-end="3856">copyeditor complaints,</p>
</li>
<li data-start="3857" data-end="3883">
<p data-start="3859" data-end="3883">journal layout breakage,</p>
</li>
<li data-start="3884" data-end="3910">
<p data-start="3886" data-end="3910">and reviewer irritation.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="3912" data-end="3935">If you want, I can now:</p>
<ul data-start="3937" data-end="4223">
<li data-start="3937" data-end="4036">
<p data-start="3939" data-end="4036">do a <strong data-start="3944" data-end="3978">global mechanical rewrite pass</strong> on your full <code data-start="3992" data-end="3998">.tex</code> file to enforce this rule everywhere,</p>
</li>
<li data-start="4037" data-end="4126">
<p data-start="4039" data-end="4126">define semantic macros like <code data-start="4067" data-end="4079">\Coherence</code>, <code data-start="4081" data-end="4088">\Flow</code>, <code data-start="4090" data-end="4100">\Entropy</code> that are line-break safe,</p>
</li>
<li data-start="4127" data-end="4223">
<p data-start="4129" data-end="4223">or prepare a <strong data-start="4142" data-end="4175">camera-ready typesetting pass</strong> (widows, orphans, spacing, equation alignment).</p>
</li>
