<p data-start="587" data-end="666">This is invalid. <code data-start="604" data-end="613">\mathbf</code>, <code data-start="615" data-end="625">\mathcal</code>, <code data-start="627" data-end="636">\mathrm</code> <strong data-start="637" data-end="665">only work inside <code data-start="656" data-end="663">$...$</code></strong>.</p>
