<p data-start="1327" data-end="1361">They <strong data-start="1332" data-end="1360">must be inside math mode</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1363" data-end="1366">
<h3 data-start="1368" data-end="1419">1.2 Unicode math symbols leaking into text mode</h3>
