Missing </span><span><span class="hljs-type">character</span></span><span>: There </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">is</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">no</span></span><span> 𝜃 (U+</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>D703)
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1530" data-end="1627">This means <strong data-start="1541" data-end="1597">Unicode Greek letters were pasted directly into text</strong>, not produced via LaTeX math.</p>
