<p data-start="1789" data-end="1821">literal <code data-start="1797" data-end="1800">θ</code>, <code data-start="1802" data-end="1805">Θ</code>, <code data-start="1807" data-end="1810">Φ</code>, <code data-start="1812" data-end="1815">≃</code>, etc.</p>
</li>
